'''Family Heirlooms''' are a variety of items a player may find in the attic minigame at the beginning of the game by searching the room with a flashlight. Once detected with the flashlight, these heirlooms will be added into the player's [[Assets]] with a brief description, estimated price value, and rarity. Players will then have the option to: Discard, Donate, Play, Refurbish or Sell Items. As of 2024, there are 182 different heirlooms. 

Certain heirlooms may give additional bonuses for your character. An example is the 'Lucky Dice', which despite has a low selling point if sold, should be kept to increase success in the [[Lottery]] and [[Casino]].

'''Note: This list is not complete as the number of heirlooms are constantly subjected to change by the developers.''' 
*This price is a list of heirlooms currently found.
*Prices may vary based on the character's country, duration in the family, and condition of the heirloom.
*Emojis depicted below will differ from heirlooms found in the game.

